{"tid":841060,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"兩度求婚】與細十歲商人秘戀十二年 薛家燕獲仔女支持","createTime":"2018-09-29T09:45:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-29T09:53:05.000Z","uid":128369,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ea744e235081385027fb4ddd7f1582571174c2f8","tid":841060,"uid":128369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T09:45:21.000Z","msg":"薛家燕喺84年同生意人石保慶結婚，婚後生咗三子女就淡出娛樂圈，專心相夫教子，惜於95年離婚，家燕姐復出工作，接job接到手軟。今年係家燕姐入行60年，連日嚟佢亦忙於宣傳同籌備喺12月舉行嘅演唱會。<br />\n<br />\n一直專心工作嘅家燕姐，鮮有戀情傳出，只係喺04年承認同電腦工程師Andy Chan發展一段姊弟戀，可惜呢段戀情維持咗一年就無疾而終。<br />\n<br />\n日前家燕姐接受《蘋果》訪問，嗰陣問佢有冇恨搵番個伴侶，佢話：「我都唔夠時間做嘢，有時夜晚餐飯都凌晨兩點幾先食，要搵個伴，唔通兩點幾食完，三點幾先見佢，個個都走人。每日開心，有好多朋友就夠啦！」(新聞連結： <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2xKwTbP\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2xKwTbP&d=Rk%2FbIM7tdILA6ESJHrBbmL%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=a1601574\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2xKwTbP</a> )"},{"pid":"4ba88a48b9a33b13cf446ef908d733fd204b0eb8","tid":841060,"uid":132587,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T09:48:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/kwan1_4999765175a7401a08f5dc-1050x630.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F02%2Fkwan1_4999765175a7401a08f5dc-1050x630.jpg&h=0ca04ab8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eb1b27add2c3386f5944890586cac54d7f932331","tid":841060,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ba88a48b9a33b13cf446ef908d733fd204b0eb8","tid":841060,"uid":132587,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T09:48:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/kwan1_4999765175a7401a08f5dc-1050x630.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fupload